author: kevin
msg: Converted oai.applib.value.Date to use Joda-time's LocalDate instead of java.util.Date.
This has gone quite far toward making the sql-store integration tests time-zone trouble free.
While it may seem heavy handed, it is consistent with mailing list comments to base the applib date, etc, on UTC, which LocalDate is, implicitly.
